{"tid":1531704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生同我入黎","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:15:53.000Z","uid":315546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e05958396518177f71e2d802c360aa164a0b910","tid":1531704,"uid":315546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"同我填左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話比關注組知我地對未來罷課嘅諗法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYWvm4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYWvm4u.png&h=f138016d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99641f631c4003206fb0c51c68aba19527d71293","tid":1531704,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68d831512d8de41e50af8060aa4ab70b104c4f9","tid":1531704,"uid":315546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0ed76179c6cfe13a440cc9ed4f6c43f907d98f","tid":1531704,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"點填"},{"pid":"20fc5dbcb425557f03af3e4bf6beb5253ecc54c9","tid":1531704,"uid":715